"Me Grimlock say let's smash!" GRIMLOCK said angrilly, "And him Swoop
say no! Him Swoop say no smash, no kill, no destruction!" GRIMLOCK's
optics began to darken again as the anger inside him threatened to
bubble forth again. "Me Grimlock give the order and he say no!"

SWOOP looked torn, "You Grimlock in charge!" he said, "But me could
not . . . " He trailed off, not sure how to articulate the rather
complex thoughts in his head.

"How do you follow the orders of a commander when he has become a
madmech."  Another voice said, this one sounding much more cultured
and refined as compared to GRIMLOCK. Although he was clearly not one
of GRIMLOCK's men he did have a resemblance to them. He was emerged
from the brush halfway between WHEELIE and GRIMLOCK.

http://tfwiki.net/wiki/Backstop_%28Cybertron%29

Behind the new figure was TERRANOTRON in robot mode.

SWOOP glanced at the new ones, "Why you here Backstop? You were
suppose to wait." he said.

"See, you find new leader!" GRIMLOCK roared at SWOOP!

SWOOP only shook his head as he stepped back his hands up defensively.

(TAG)

- Preston
